Beneath Retro Mode Is Out Now: https://store.playstation.com/concept/10013555

Beneath is a Lovecraft-inspired survival FPS from a micro studio founded by two brothers, with a lifelong passion in horror and shooters. 

Bringing you bleeding edge visuals (circa 1998) the Beneath retro mode brings the same combat, the same oppressive deep sea horror, but reborn in glorious low resolution... which really adds a distinct charm to the nightmare filled research stations.

Monster Hunter Wilds is the next generation of the acclaimed Monster Hunter series.
